name: Insight
description: This is Maxim Kuznetsov genesis piece on Hic Et Nunc. Beyond Light is a series of unique abstract artworks exploring the nature of light and color and their relationship to human psychology and personal experience. Insight is a representation of a sudden thought penetrating your mind. If you don't grab it in time, it will pass by. Edition of 40. 1800 x 1800 px.
